data.description: Check out this beautifully priced to sell home with No HOA. This home has 4 bedroom, With 2 of the bedrooms being Primary bedrooms. 3 full bathrooms, 2 car garage. Split floor plan with an open concept in the main area of the home that offers a wood burning fireplace in the living room. Breakfast bar and a conveniently located laundry room. All appliances convey with sale of home.  New HVAC installed in 2023. Interior has new paint, and kitchen cabinets have fresh stain. Established landscaping with a new Bee Hive Watering system that can be controlled from an app on your smart phone. A 13X10 Sears shed with wood floor in back yard. This home is also comes with a home warranty plan until Nov. 2024. Close to entertainment, shopping, medical, and schools. This home is truly a must see.
